<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038419" n="147r"/>
<p>
               <lb/>Debitas Tibi ago gratias <add>tum</add> pro transmissione <rs key="B_1718-04-09_991170457446705501" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Nicolaus I Bernoulli von 1718.04.09</note> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei,
               <lb/>tum pro humanissima Tua <rs type="letter">responsione</rs><!--brieftag--> ad ultimas meas <rs key="B_1718-03-19_991170517055905501" type="letter">litte<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ras</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Nicolaus I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti von 1718.03.19</note> <expan><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></expan> <date>19. Marti<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></date> datas. Quando dixi me non intelligere, quo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>modo Problema illud de<del> veloc</del> determinanda velocitate liquoris
               <lb/>per canalem flexilem data vi constanter projecti, applicari
               <lb/>possit velocitati sanguinis per arterias fluentis, eo quod in dila<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatione cordis nulla fiat in arterias sanguinis i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>issio; opinio
               <lb/>mea fuit, non quod tum sanguinis cursus pereat, sed quod non
               <lb/>semper sanguis eadem cum velocitate in orificia arteriarum in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>grediatur, aut quod arteri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non semper usque ad orificium ple<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>n<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint fluento sanguinis,<subst><del>adeoque</del><add>et per consequens</add></subst><note type="editorial">In der nachträglich eingefügten Textpartie steht zusätzlich ein "quod", das durch ein überflüssiges und daher in der Transkription weggelassenes "per" überschrieben ist.</note> hujus motus non semper
               <lb/>sit <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quabilis sed modo velocior, modo remissior; unde adhuc
               <pb facs="1038421" n="147v"/>
<lb/>dum non intelligo, quomodo <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielminus</rs> potuerit dicere,
               <lb/>quod <cit><quote><hi rend="u">feriante corde fluentum sanguinis perenni et unifor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mi agitatione continuo et continenter sua vasa discurrat</hi></quote></cit>.
               <lb/>Videtur enim ipse pulsus arteriarum indicare, quod h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
               <lb/>agitatio sanguinis non sit continuo uniformis, sed modo for<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tior modo remissior. Quare Te rogo, ut si forte <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs>
<lb/>meo <subst><del><unclear>probam</unclear></del><add>plenam</add></subst> et cum sententia <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmini</rs> conspirantem
               <lb/>Problematis hujus solutionem acceperis, eam mecum
               <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicare digneris. Ego libenter accipiam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad
               <lb/><rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">exercitationem</rs> Tuam de secretione fluidorum spectantia 
               <lb/>ad me mittes, et diligenter exequar omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> jubebis.
               <lb/><abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mum</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Exc.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Procuratorem <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolum</rs><note type="editorial">Tiepolo, Lorenzo (1673-1742)</note> <add>domi su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> salutavi,
               <lb/>qui me maxima cum humanitate excepit; rursusque
               <lb/>antequam hinc abeat ipsi devotum honoris cultum et de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bita obsequia offeram.
            </p>
<closer><salute><del>D </del>Vale et fave.</salute> <dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place"><abbr>Patav.</abbr></rs> <date when="1718-05-02">2. Maji 1718</date>.</dateline>
</closer>
<postscript>
<p>
<lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Quoniam mihi dictum fuit, <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mos</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Exc.<hi rend="sup">mos</hi></abbr> <abbr>Dnos</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930 pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1089586175" type="persons">Reformatores</rs><note type="editorial">Von 3.10.1716-4.11.1717 waren die Moderatoren der Universität Padua Giovanni Pietro Pasqualigo (1667-1718 [?]; das Datum der GND ist unwahrscheinlich, da er noch ein weiteres Jahr als Riformator amtiert), Michele Morosini di Lorenzo, Cavaliere (1670-1751) und Francesco Soranzo (17./18. Jh.)</note> haud facile consensuros esse in constitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>endo successore <abbr>Dni</abbr> Abbatis <rs key="pers_DE-588-104058412" type="person">Viali</rs> uno ex duobus Com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>petitoribus, <rs key="pers_DE-588-109091766X" type="person">Riva</rs><note type="editorial">Riva, Lodovico (1698-1746)</note> nempe et <rs key="pers_DE-588-117689610" type="person">Pontedera</rs>; sed posse for<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tassis contingere, ut hanc Cathedram dent tertio
                  <lb/>cuidam; idcirco Te rogo, ut Amicis Tuis Celeberri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerum</rs> nostrum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endes, cujus Agrosto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><rs key="biblio_FTUNNEH6" type="biblio">graphi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Scheuchzer, Johannes, Agrostographi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Helvetic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> prodromus sistens binas graminum Alpinorum hactenus non descriptorum, et quorundam ambiguorum decades, [Zürich] 1708.</note> specimen <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924399" type="person">Capello</rs> dedicatum haud
                  <lb/>dubie vidisti.<note type="comment">In diesem Postscriptum wird zum ersten Mal im Briefwechsel zwischen Nicolaus I Bernolli und Pietro Antonio Michelotti die künftige Bewerbung Joahnn Scheuchzers um den Lehrstuhl der Botanik in Padua angesprochen. Die hier erwähnten Mitbewerber, Lodovico Riva und Giulio Pontedero, sind  insbesondere auch im Brief von Nicolaus I Bernoulli an Johannes Scheuchzer von 1719.02.04 erwähnt.</note>
</p>
</postscript>
